                     <h4>Talkmos Privacy Policy</h4> 
                     <p>Your privacy is important to Talkmos (“Talkmos,” “we,” “us,” “our”). Talkmos has created this Privacy Policy (“Privacy Policy”) to demonstrate the commitment to protecting your privacy and to explain the personal data Talkmos processes, how Talkmos processes it, and for what purposes. It also describes the choices available to you regarding our use of your personal information and how you can access and update this information.</p>
